scenes.description: Mori Calliope talks about her family visiting Japan and her album's release on the main stage.
Mori Calliope uses a handheld 'jidori' (selfie) camera to show different angles of her 3D model and the stage.
Mori Calliope returns to the main stage and gives final thanks to her fans and staff.
